node.text:
Wild Animals🐾 are usually very used to ticks🕷 and they naturally just live with them until they fall off or go over to another animal!🤷🏼‍♂️ But in some cases when there are to many Ticks on one spot they can cause bad wounds!🤕 These open wounds then serve as a perfect ground for flies to lay eggs and eventually the host (in this case Chuckie) can end up with a deadly infection!😓 (If not treated)
•
Through my close relationship with Chuckie🥰 I immediately spotted the issue and decided to give her a helping hand with it, before it gets worse!💪🏼The strong bond & trust I have with Chuckie or even the Lions🦁 is a HUGE advantage in such situations! Instead of making them go through a stressful process with the Vets including Anesthetics💉 , I can just sort out such issues in a playful way without them even realizing that something’s wrong!😂💪🏼
•
Use YOUR Power, YOUR Advantage, YOUR Knowledge, YOUR Qualities to help Others, cause true Happiness is not found in what you get from someone but in what you give to someone!🙏🏼❤️
•
Tag 3 People who need to Watch this Video🎥 and READ this Caption!🤓
•
& Let me know what YOU think, in the Comments below👇🏼

Since I physically💪🏼 can‘t compete with them during feeding sessions and also in certain other situations where they dominate each other, I will never be able to become head of the pride! I will always remain on Eye-Level👁 with them! I will always be Loved❤️ & Respected🙏🏼 but the Rules are made by them!🤷🏼‍♂️

By being part of a Lion-Pride🦁 it is a "MUST" for me to socialize and spend time with them even when its, wet🌧, cold🥶, dirty💩 and uncomfortable.🥴 We humans often choose to take the easiest way but we forget that ease is a greater threat to progress and success than hardship☝🏼. Deep relationships are built in the toughest times and not only when there’s sunshine☀️ & rainbows🌈. Having that said, to be honest: A stormy & rainy day is often much appreciated by the lions more than by us humans.😅 With this Video I simply wanted to give you an insight👀 into the life of Lions on a Day which is not warm and hot but rather wet & cold.🙌🏼

Wild Animals🐾 are usually very used to ticks🕷 and they naturally just live with them until they fall off or go over to another animal!🤷🏼‍♂️ But in some cases when there are to many Ticks on one spot they can cause bad wounds!🤕 These open wounds then serve as a perfect ground for flies to lay eggs and eventually the host (in this case Chuckie) can end up with a deadly infection!😓 (If not treated)
•
Through my close relationship with Chuckie🥰 I immediately spotted the issue and decided to give her a helping hand with it, before it gets worse!💪🏼The strong bond & trust I have with Chuckie or even the Lions🦁 is a HUGE advantage in such situations! Instead of making them go through a stressful process with the Vets including Anesthetics💉 , I can just sort out such issues in a playful way without them even realizing that something’s wrong!😂💪🏼
•
Use YOUR Power, YOUR Advantage, YOUR Knowledge, YOUR Qualities to help Others, cause true Happiness is not found in what you get from someone but in what you give to someone!🙏🏼❤️

But how did you manage to become Part of their Family⁉️ This is the most asked Question of people who discover Me🙋🏼‍♂️ and my life with the Animals.🐾🙌🏼 The answer is actually pretty simple: Next to respect, love & understanding the fundamental part is to "Be There"! Being there at all times "especially" in the bad😰 & rough👊🏼 times makes you part of the family🙏🏼
•
We all have so many Friends when things are going well👌🏼 when we got Money💰, Status😎, Power💪🏼 & Influence🗣 than the World🌍 is Your very Best Friend!🤗 The question is: Who is there when things go downhill📉, when things get tough🥵 and Your not on the winning side anymore❓ The ones who then are still standing by your side, supporting You and are being there for You, those are the ones You will count to your FAMILY!🙏🏼❤️
•
It‘s no different with the animals🤷🏼‍♂️
•

node.text:
⚠️BREAKING NEWS⚠️ Today the Journey of a true WARRIOR⚔️ came to an End! A few hours ago in the afternoon (Friday the 11th of June 2021 at 1pm) The most Famous wild Lion🦁 on Our Planet🌍 took his last breath. He was the biggest Celebrity of the Maasai Mara in Kenya🇰🇪 and a true inspiration for millions of people around the World.🙌🏼 His story combined with his look makes him a true legend and the Undisputed ‚‘‘King of the Jungle‘‘!😲
•
How did he get His famous SCAR?
•
Scarface earned his nickname through an injury in 2012 when he lost his right eyelid👁 while taking over a territory with his three brothers Hunter, Sikio, and Morani.👊🏼 They won the territorial fight and took over the ‚‘‘Marsh Pride‘‘ females after defeating the lesser males which they killed or sent packing.⚔️ He ruled for several Years together with his Brothers over an immense Territory🙌🏼 and they were challenged repeatedly but all the challengers failed, the legends have defended their territory and prides with all their might for over eight years which is an incredible accomplishment out there in the wild!😲 Scarface🦁 will never be forgotten for what he has done for the Maasai Mara but instead remembered forever as a legend, an icon and one of the greatest of all time.🙏🏼❤️ His Brothers are now continuing his legacy!👊🏼💪🏼⚔️
•
Share this Post to let the World🌍 know about the loss of this true Wild Warrior and help me to touch Millions of Hearts❤️ by telling his Story!🙏🏼
•
Comment Your personal Toughts below!👇🏼
•

⚠️READ THIS CAPTION⚠️ & SWIPE LEFT‼️ People are amazed of my bond with Dexter🦁 & the Lion Pride.🙌🏼 But let me tell you something: Establishing a true bond with a Spotted Hyena🐺 and adapting to their behavior is way more difficult! Spotted Hyenas have an incredible complex way of communication and socialization within a clan🤯 and understanding them was one of the biggest Challenges and Achievements in my Life.🙏🏼
•
I searched🔎 through all the hard drives, memory cards and my own phone📲 for different "unseen" pictures & videos which should give you an Idea of how long the way was up until today where I can walk into the home and space of a fully grown Spotted Hyena🐾 and share love with her. ❤️ This is not a bond You can create over night or with a few visits to a petting zoo.☝🏼 This has come a looong way with lots of ups and downs and I was there from Day one when Chuckie was a little fluffy playful thing🐣 up until today where things can get serious and he became a massive🙌🏼, powerful💪🏼 and dangerous predator.😲
•

When I told others about my Dreams & My Mission 3-4 Years ago at the very first they laughed😂, then they doubted🧐 me, then they hated😈 and now they ADMIRE!🦁😲
•
People will always doubt YOU and laugh at your dreams & goals! You‘re not the only one 🤗 This happened to Me in the Past and is still happening now.🤷🏼‍♂️ But the greatest feeling ever is the Day you can prove them wrong! 💪🏼🙌🏼
•
Stay focused! Work Hard! & Never give up!
